	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-175207021" class="story-title"> <a   href="//tech.slashdot.org/story/24/10/07/1938237/the-slow-death-of-the-hyperlink">The Slow Death of the Hyperlink</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.halifaxexaminer.ca/beyond-the-link-tax-journalism-and-the-changing-nature-of-the-internet/"  title="External link - https://www.halifaxexaminer.ca/beyond-the-link-tax-journalism-and-the-changing-nature-of-the-internet/" target="_blank"> (halifaxexaminer.ca) </a></span></span>

		
		
